    {
        "id": "world_truth_ip_foreshadow",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_ai_truth.mp4",
        "speaker": "AI亚里士多德",
        "text": "其中，流传度最广、认知最深刻的故事——比如你们那个时代的动漫、游戏——会形成强大的'故事原型'，甚至可以被万象行者借用其力量。",
        "next": "world_truth_ip_foreshadow_jiao_jiao"
    },
    {
        "id": "world_truth_ip_foreshadow_jiao_jiao",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_ai_truth.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "没错！就像是我最喜欢的那些动漫和游戏！原来我平时玩游戏也是在为成为万象行者做准备呀！嘿嘿！",
        "next": "heroine_mission_explanation_1"
    },
    {
        "id": "heroine_mission_explanation_1",
        "type": "dialogue",
        "background": "game/videos/cg/cg_awakening_partnership.mp4",
        "speaker": "魏娇娇",
        "text": "没错！我们就是故事的守护者！虽然我还是新手……",
        "next": "walker_awakening_1"
